# Title: Remote Thread Creation Via PowerShell In Uncommon Target
# Author: Florian Roth (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2018-06-25
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects the creation of a remote thread from a Powershell process in an uncommon target process
# MITRE Tactic: Defense Evasion
# Tags: attack.defense-evasion, attack.execution, attack.t1218.011, attack.t1059.001
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/create_remote_thread/create_remote_thread_win_powershell_susp_targets.yml

SourceImage IN ("*\\powershell.exe", "*\\pwsh.exe") TargetImage IN ("*\\rundll32.exe", "*\\regsvr32.exe")